views.text: The UK’s original and biggest independent bus times app is back - and better than ever. We don’t just show you where and when your bus is coming, now you can buy a ticket for it too.  There’s more real time information then ever before - live moving buses on the map, live departures and service info and route maps. And with new m-Tickets for your favourite operators, you can plan, book and pay for your journey all in one single app. It’s no wonder that Bus Checker powers more than 100 million journeys every year across the globe.
